When you do a simple query for all unreleased versions in a project it generates the following JQL  {code}project=HSP1 and in unreleasedVersions(){code}, the unreleasedVersions then searches all projects - to improve performance we should generate the JQL  {code}project=HSP1 and in unreleasedVersions(HSP1){code}

