There's currently a way to add, delete and get info about a user using the SOAP interface, but no way to modify them or their info. An example situation would be if a company has changed names and everyone's email addresses need to be changed. The only real way to accomplish that at the moment is to export to XML, manually modify everything, then reimport it, which is very prone to error.

